cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as word segmentation. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it proposes a new neural model for the task. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it utilizes a long short-term memory (LSTM) architecture. Finally, it could also be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as word segmentation is an important task in information retrieval systems.
